{
  "annotations": [
    {
      "start_time": 2,
      "end_time": 27,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "There's the affirmation and then there's the permission. I've been finding work that I've been interested in Audrey Lorde's work and about the uses of the erotic and but then I read it and I'm like oh, no, it's about life. It's the same thing. It's about saying yes ..."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Gesel Mason",
          "category": "People"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "bc95f237-9604-4e53-9a6e-fe06bb98a600"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 27,
      "end_time": 27,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Yeah."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Bebe Miller",
          "category": "People"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "1cafd736-9564-4174-a39b-c05be20b8317"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 27,
      "end_time": 32,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "... To your passion. It's about joy and chaos."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Gesel Mason",
          "category": "People"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "0235b503-90ba-40de-a6d1-396424b2f1ef"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 32,
      "end_time": 34,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Yeah."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Bebe Miller",
          "category": "People"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "80d561f0-d35c-4594-ad24-5d0a92062fb4"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 34,
      "end_time": 74,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "It's been co-opted by the, there's a way that society has defined it, ans it's like, \"No, I don't have to do it that way. There's another way to say yes to this thing.\" It's like, we're all just doing the same thing. It's like trying to find the yes, the truth about something, and each one of us has a different way of going about that and it includes our backgrounds in cultures. I think there's something both about permission and affirmation and working with each of the choreographers and there's also something beautiful about I'm working with folks who have been making this work for 30 years."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Gesel Mason",
          "category": "People"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "611a4a6b-ee6f-44fe-97d0-cdb87052a437"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 74,
      "end_time": 76,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Mm-hmm (affirmative)."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Bebe Miller",
          "category": "People"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "a029faf9-1934-4887-89ff-d05b6701200c"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 76,
      "end_time": 79,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "It's like, \"Oh, you could keep doing it.\""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Gesel Mason",
          "category": "People"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "f941f65a-48d6-4946-a9a6-8620e5f2f16d"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 79,
      "end_time": 79,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Yeah."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Bebe Miller",
          "category": "People"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "4c3313d3-4519-4c05-8d59-42267f141a84"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 79,
      "end_time": 94,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "You can keep going. You can keep asking those questions, you can keep not knowing, you can keep being curious, there's no like sort of arrival. It's just, and that's heartening."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Gesel Mason",
          "category": "People"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "17cde1b0-dd5b-4c59-b2af-f699e67351c5"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 94,
      "end_time": 95,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Mm-hmm (affirmative), yeah."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Bebe Miller",
          "category": "People"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "82d1ab7c-2ff8-482d-afe6-68a084fb845e"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 95,
      "end_time": 140,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "We were also having a conversation about like in our field, it's often, next, next, next, new, new, new and what happens when you're mid-career, and what happens when you're like legacy, and established, and in a field, particularly the modern dance field or whatever we're calling it now a days, and this interest in the new and the next, but there's also something about the deeper and the wider, you know, things expanding versus just, what is in our history that is also important. Thanks to the shoulders also move, you know?"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Gesel Mason",
          "category": "People"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "78e0036f-dd8f-4b21-b15f-77334bba085f"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 140,
      "end_time": 141,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Yeah."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Bebe Miller",
          "category": "People"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "a9c96991-5ef2-45dc-ac1d-b6649158d236"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 141,
      "end_time": 142,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "They don't just stay in one place, you know."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Gesel Mason",
          "category": "People"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "22f496b4-7ff9-42e5-9e23-0ffbcb6c9586"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 142,
      "end_time": 143,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Yeah."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Bebe Miller",
          "category": "People"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "e61c4e77-716c-4a82-b182-c79975f069a2"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 143,
      "end_time": 155,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "They also move, and what information do they hold. I don't want to just keep, now, this project is about to end and so I'm also like giving myself space to be like ..."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Gesel Mason",
          "category": "People"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "c9bd4144-fdc4-4b3c-b4ca-7c5ab6879128"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 155,
      "end_time": 156,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Don't know. Yeah, sure."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Bebe Miller",
          "category": "People"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "7b2d0427-8873-4359-abbc-0420d07ea95c"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 156,
      "end_time": 158,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Don't know."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
